title: LF MID and BOT Lane for Go4Lol on Sunday (Plat)
body:
We are searching for the Midlane and Botlane positions for the upcoming Go4LoL tournemant on sunday the 5th april 2015.
We are Germans so Germans are prefered but we speak decent English aswell.
The age doesn't really matter as long as you are not twelve or something.
I am diamond 4 at the moment and my friend is plat 5.
Just add me ingame for further information: TSM Ocko

replies.body: still searching for a mid laner
